## Comparison of Major Generative AI Models

| Model           | Main Strength                         | Common Applications                    |
| --------------- | ------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| Transformer     | Language understanding and generation | Chatbots, translation, code generation |
| VAE             | Learning latent representations       | Compression, anomaly detection         |
| GAN             | Realistic image generation            | Face generation, image enhancement     |
| Diffusion Model | High-quality content generation       | Image generation, medical imaging      |

